<section id="fs-idm370587920" class="exercise-set-a">
<exercise id="fs-idm358890368">
<problem id="fs-idm371502704">
<para id="fs-idm375576800"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67943"/>Indicate whether each statement describes financial accounting or managerial accounting.</para>
<list id="fs-idm377362128" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>The information is directed at external users who are making decisions pertaining to investing, extending credit, and other decisions.</item>
<item>The principal users are the organization’s managers.</item>
<item>The key focus is on the entity as a whole.</item>
<item>The rules and principles are very flexible.</item>
<item>The information gathered is usually available after an independent audit has been completed.</item>
</list>
</problem>
